    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Paper Pilot</h2>Immerse yourself in the thrilling adventure of <strong>Paper Pilot</strong>, where you control the &quot;Paper Pilot&quot; and fly through 15 unique levels. Your goal is to complete each level and collect the star boxes to unlock new levels. But be careful! Your gun can overheat, so you'll need to develop your own strategy to navigate this unique adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/a35716620115a3c072afbfad3759ada1.poster.avif?t=1727719074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/a35716620115a3c072afbfad3759ada1.webm?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/a35716620115a3c072afbfad3759ada1.mp4?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>15 Exciting Levels:</strong> Explore diverse worlds and master different challenges.<br>    </li><li><strong>Collect Star Boxes:</strong> Unlock new levels by finding the coveted star boxes in each level.<br>    </li><li><strong>Overheating Weapons:</strong> Be mindful of your weapon's heat and plan your shots strategically.<br>    </li><li><strong>Unique Flight Mechanics:</strong> Experience a one-of-a-kind flight adventure with intuitive controls.<br>    </li><li><strong>Atmospheric Graphics:</strong> Enjoy hand-drawn graphics and detailed environments.<br>    </li><li><strong>Challenging Obstacles:</strong> Test your skills and develop clever strategies to overcome all obstacles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/aee8599df3f27ee98b1730f60eb4145d.poster.avif?t=1727719074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/aee8599df3f27ee98b1730f60eb4145d.webm?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/aee8599df3f27ee98b1730f60eb4145d.mp4?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Machinegun</h2>Shoot the obstacles with your machine gun, but be careful with your heat<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engine</h2>Upgrade your engine in the hangar to fly with more control<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Heat</h2>Upgrade your heat management to shoot for a longer time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/91cdba72f463182aee27ae7650ea7960.poster.avif?t=1727719074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/91cdba72f463182aee27ae7650ea7960.webm?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/91cdba72f463182aee27ae7650ea7960.mp4?t=1727719074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hangar</h2>In the hangar you can do the following things:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock new planes and change your skin<br></li><li>You have different weapons like a bomb or the shotgun which can be drop to destroy<br></li><li>Earn coins and unlock different upgrades, like the engine, gun and heat off your plane.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083600/extras/f246ef130a46f9f4b83a86791fc6e15c.avif?t=1727719074\" width=512 height=288 /></span>",
